{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/\uff08\u65e0\u5b57\uff09\u4e3b\u827a\u672fslogan.png?t=1739280097\" /><br><br><strong>Vine Card is a deck-building strategic game with roguelike elements. <br>Choose from a roster of quirky heroes with even quirkier skills, <br>plan your route around the game board, <br>grab the goodies and defeat the baddies!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/EN\u6807\u98981.png?t=1739280097\" /><br>Navigate your hero around a game board of limited grids, one step at a time. <br>Sounds boring? Well, throw in a deck of 200+ unique cards, and watch the chemical reactions happen. <br>8 playable characters with wildly different styles/skills further increase the fun.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/01\u6218\u68cb+\u5361\u724c+\u8089\u9e3d\uff0c\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u3002.gif?t=1739280097\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/EN\u6807\u98982.png?t=1739280097\" /><br>It all starts from this fictitious empire on a fictitious planet. The Tang Empire is facing a pivotal moment and from there, things start to go wild. <br>Follow our heroes from the Tang Empire to the Far West, then the mysterious Skyland descending from the, duh, sky! <br>Embark on a journey that is natural, semi-natural, supernatural, meta-natural, and unnatural at the same time! <br>Blend Wuxia and science fiction and fantasy and mythology together and it just works.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/02\u539f\u521b\u6545\u4e8b\uff0c\u67b6\u7a7a\u5386\u53f2\u3002.gif?t=1739280097\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/EN\u6807\u98983.png?t=1739280097\" /><br>Take elements from Chinese mythology, Norse mythology, Celtic mythology, Arthurian mythology, Cthulhu mythology (yeah, we've got that covered, too), add modern pop culture, sprinkle a liberal dose of actual history, serve while hot.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/03\u6587\u5316\u4e71\u7096\uff0c\u65e2\u8981\u4e5f\u8981\uff01.gif?t=1739280097\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/EN\u6807\u98984.png?t=1739280097\" /><br>Gatling guns vs swords vs crossbows vs pretty much anything you can think of. <br>Who said cowboys can't do Chinese kungfu, eh? Leave common sense behind, dude. It's holding you down.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/04\u793c\u5d29\u4e50\u574f\uff1f\u529f\u6cd5\u9601\u548c\u519b\u706b\u5e93\uff01.gif?t=1739280097\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/EN\u6807\u98985.png?t=1739280097\" /><br>The game comes with 30+ handcrafted &quot;legend site&quot; stages, from the mysterious Sanxingdui to the isle of Avalon to the glorious Valhalla. <br>Take a break from the busy combat and solve these special challenges instead!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/05\u540d\u80dc\u53e4\u8ff9\uff0c\u673a\u5173\u91cd\u91cd\u3002.gif?t=1739280097\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Fledgling","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2649800/4d3d65d180ba32ecf3a4d7c8091691af50d0da21.jpg"},{"name":"Dragon Dance","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2649800/748b0e6e57d71d469e69b6755f920d64c31a433d.jpg"},{"name":"M